                <a class="collapsed user-guide-title" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#image-tuning"><h3 class="user-guide-title">Image Tuning</h3></a>
                <div id="image-tuning" class="image-tuning collapse user-guide-subsection">

                    <p>The default settings of the <strong>360fly 4K</strong> camera are optimized to deliver the highest quality output within a wide range of environments and lighting conditions. To get the most out of your videos and images, the <strong>360fly 4K</strong> offers advanced options that will allow you to fine-tune your camera’s settings.</p>
