                    <p><strong>Brightness:</strong> The <img src="<?php echo $skinUrl; ?>images/user-guide/camera-brightness.png" class="user-guide-img" alt="Camera Brightness"/> slider fine-tunes the brightness of the subjects within your image without affecting your camera’s exposure compensation.</p>
