                    <p><strong>Contrast:</strong> Increase the <img src="<?php echo $skinUrl; ?>images/user-guide/camera-contrast.png" class="user-guide-img" alt="Camera Contrast"/> setting to achieve a more vivid picture or lower the setting to deliver a slightly flatter appearance.</p>
